    <abstract>
      <t>The BGP Monitoring Protocol (BMP) [RFC7854] is designed to monitor BGP [RFC4271] running status, such as BGP peer relationship establishment and termination and route updates. This document provides a use case that the BMP station can get all BGP capability information of the monitored network device via BMP.</t>
